{
  "doc_id": "14529",
  "text": "These features associated with the biocompatibility of PL are essential for the development of delivery systems [CITATION_1] for treatment of multidrug-resistant bacteria. In addition, the use of PL with different hydrophilic-lipophilic balance (HLB) [CITATION_2] such as PL 407 and PL 403, PL 407 and PL L-81, PL 108 and PL 403, and PL 108 and PL L-81 as binary systems can be an interesting alternative to modulate the biopharmaceutical profile of these formulations [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] [CITATION_7] .",
